public static interface StatementBuilder.OngoingReadingWithoutWhere extends StatementBuilder.OngoingReading, ExposesHints, ExposesWhere<StatementBuilder.OngoingReadingWithWhere>, ExposesMatch, StatementBuilder.ExposesExistentialSubqueryCall
A match that exposes returning and where methods to add required information. While the where clause is optional, a returning clause needs to be specified before the statement can be build.
